item.title: 【Requests】[REQ CAP] - Capital Jingle Bell Ball 2023, Dec 9-10 - Live stream
item.description:
Barclaycard, Global and Outernet London will live stream Capital’s Jingle Bell Ball with Barclaycard at an epic watch party on Saturday 9th and Sunday 10th December, live from Outernet from 6pm on both days.

The free event will be a fully immersive digital experience, creating a snowy winter wonderland for visitors, with performances streamed live from the UK’s biggest Christmas party at The O2 via Global Player. The livestream will be accompanied by an interactive Snow Globe experience with a photographer on hand to snap photos of guests for an instant digital takeaway of themselves. There will be a seating area to enjoy the show, a hot chocolate stand and Capital’s Jingle Bell Ball merchandise giveaways for Barclaycard customers.

Confirmed artists include Alicia Keys, Take That, Tom Grennan, Becky Hill, Busted, Rita Ora, and more. The performances will be streamed at the heart of Outernet. With full directional surround studio sound, viewers will experience a front row seat at the UK’s Biggest Christmas Party!

Capital’s Jingle Bell Ball with Barclaycard will also be live streamed on Global Player, and as part of Global’s partnership with ITV, ITV1 and ITVX, there will be a special broadcast featuring all the best bits later in December.
